
%^RED%^Houses are currently unavailable.%^RESET%^

A player may own a house anywhere on the main continent, as long
as there is room for it. Each town has a 'housing district' where 
houses may be built if you wish your house to be in a town. 
  
    One room house:   75,000 gold
    Extra rooms:      25,000 gold each
    Lockable rooms:   50,000 gold
    
If you are interested in buying a house, please speak to one of 
the staff. You can get a 10% discount if you have the knowledge
and wish to 'build' the house yourself.
